The '''crash site memorial''', also known as the '''"community" junk yard''', was part of the wreckage of the [[Colony ship/Legends|colony ship]] [[Dowager Queen/Legends|''Dowager Queen'']]. The memorial was placed directly in front of the entrance to the [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Mos Eisley Cantina]], and stood as a monument for local residents. Many visitors left junk at the memorial for [[Jawa/Legends|Jawas]] and other scavengers to salvage.

